{"tid":386903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"24小時無食野 餓到手軟腳軟 食兩粒二寶即刻有番能量","createTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T17:23:06.000Z","uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0755a300f26c53277a5d2c3c95015811ce08570","tid":386903,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋到?"},{"pid":"cd4872c491eeeefb49897399e8f7b640ca53abc9","tid":386903,"uid":80481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"安慰劑"},{"pid":"b3cffe5f0d310a40b82f476fc55f213776d7e31c","tid":386903,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"糖"},{"pid":"d2ca9f45979ea186c5a475b7d0cfeffbb11c6654","tid":386903,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"2278a3f43aa43193e27bf71c74bc6fde68f5e30f","tid":386903,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35e219bcb4c42c223ec15a5c42576358f2ec5eff","tid":386903,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖有carbohydrates <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食野淨靠幾粒二寶會有咩後果"},{"pid":"77f5fb8080ff7cf0969f96cf1fc4ef74623ca8d0","tid":386903,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>糖有carbohydrates <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食野淨靠幾粒二寶會有咩後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02b9ba704439d0d764a3c199617db46df2fdeee","tid":386903,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>糖有carbohydrates <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食野淨靠幾粒二寶會有咩後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有carbohydrates"},{"pid":"ed25b71582ad7b5ac666521baa79b23376b808b6","tid":386903,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2c80a0465a9227c182550851146e48d2028728e","tid":386903,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddf1ee6495300fd62526fca42f4197f816aad38c","tid":386903,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"多左血糖供應比個腦<br />\n9up"},{"pid":"8e404bdaa20bfa9aa8ab2d5ed9cfc5e3161e7844","tid":386903,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>糖有carbohydrates <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食野淨靠幾粒二寶會有咩後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有carbohydrates</blockquote><br />\n唔夠每日carbohydrates 攝取量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨食二寶會點"},{"pid":"e3e924258e2fa69023bc2c13ff5090ef3a7a26fd","tid":386903,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbce1540e4ba7e8526319431b5d722306c8cebc1","tid":386903,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>糖有carbohydrates <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食野淨靠幾粒二寶會有咩後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有carbohydrates</blockquote><br />\n唔夠每日carbohydrates 攝取量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨食二寶會點</blockquote><br />\n可以吊住條命，唔會死，但會營養不良</blockquote><br />\n但有carbohydrates"}]}